snippet: After all the battles and hard graft chasing the world number one spot, Briton Andy Murray arrived there without hitting a ball on Saturday as Milos Raonic pulled out of their Paris Masters semi-final due to a leg injury....
lead_paragraph: After all the battles and hard graft chasing the world number one spot, Briton Andy Murray arrived there without hitting a ball on Saturday as Milos Raonic pulled out of their Paris Masters semi-final due to a leg injury.

headline.print_headline: Murray Is New World No. 1 After Raonic Withdraws
headline.main: Murray Is New World No. 1 After Raonic Withdraws
